{"tid":1600753,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"一句講晒 聽日和理定勇武","createTime":"2019-09-28T17:30:43.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-28T18:56:24.000Z","uid":74083,"like":44,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"1756b62f6b31e01b07c9303912ad320767040beb","tid":1600753,"uid":74083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-28T17:30:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />和理<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />勇武"},{"pid":"ec3a48f6cd9d109e203c826cb4684cacb860d137","tid":1600753,"uid":38904,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-28T17:32:12.000Z","msg":"兄弟爬山<br />\n各自努力<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/smile.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b179ff248958680450c5fad925f0386ef6a76e8b","tid":1600753,"uid":288351,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-28T17:32:41.000Z","msg":"減少被捕風險等10。1玩"},{"pid":"93da24da9e9ef0255825c8d24f8360380e698778","tid":1600753,"uid":258696,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-28T17:33:16.000Z","msg":"Mon po黑警自己估下聽日會點<br />\n人權法就pass無人驚你地<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">香港人！！<br />\n<br />\n政府已經怕左美國人權法<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n係度扮會回應普選訴求<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n但唔好忘記共產黨係信唔過既盜國賊<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n只有香港自治/香港獨立先可以得到5大訴求！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />929 全球反共<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />101 慶佢老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">香港自治，主權在民！<br />\n拯救香港，打倒共黨！<br />\n光復香港，時代革命！<br />\n香港獨立，還政於民！</span></span>"},{"pid":"53a530f5c05984a83bdfdde264d2f1fc9745c499","tid":1600753,"uid":94199,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-28T17:41:49.000Z","msg":"勇"},{"pid":"af873df95d14e5f3099ef02a2b9658ea90d239ad","tid":1600753,"uid":74083,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-28T17:48:46.000Z","msg":"本人認為和理優<br />\n鑑於聽日係connect 全球嘅反共遊行<br />\n我地應該進行外國最鍾意嘅左膠和理非游行<br />\n有成100 200 萬人去和平集會<br />\n咁先make noice 去connect 其他國家<br />\n<br />\n家下啲狗一定會用儘一切方法去刺激你地<br />\n引你地去對待 起衝突<br />\n但我希望各位唔好失焦<br />\n要先對準政權<br />\n展示出姿態去反抗呢個全球最大嘅惡勢力<br />\n<br />\n咁多位願唔願意忍一日做和理非左膠<br />\n之後10 1 你想點慶祝都得<br />\n<br />\n有其他意見都可以提出"},{"pid":"15cf97e9b8f0cd7c55653f7ff6b2b23b8a1901cf","tid":1600753,"uid":74083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"53a530f5c05984a83bdfdde264d2f1fc9745c499","tid":1600753,"uid":94199,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-28T17:41:49.000Z","msg":"勇"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-28T17:50:13.000Z","msg":"手足有咩見解<br />\n討論下"},{"pid":"941131c294e57656cde094b5dcbdb85972edd626","tid":1600753,"uid":164585,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-28T17:51:32.000Z","msg":"無記錯9月頭開始 個個都話留力10月1 <br />\n依家又問和定勇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />又想留力到幾時<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a20143c1b84f42e7d6af9c4d2aa96747cb7b3c15","tid":1600753,"uid":3302,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-28T17:52:14.000Z","msg":"和定勇係要睇警犬 唔係睇我地<br />\n班狗聽日又拉女仔入新屋嶺輪姦咪勇<br />\n唔出現咪和平遊行囉"},{"pid":"5ee45b0ad27aa4c4563787b1de4fdad2edd004c2","tid":1600753,"uid":60